{"tid":1816542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九月濕地公園輕鐵站刑毀案　警：再拘一人　搜出 31 個玻璃樽 89 張現金券","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T10:40:20.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f347cba8cdb355e7c28f6e3d90b27a580e77922","tid":1816542,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:05:19.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科今天下午再公佈一段短片，解釋氣油彈的禍害及可能帶來刑責。片中透露警方昨天拘捕一名 20 歲男子，涉嫌和去年 9 月 7 日濕地公園輕鐵站刑事毀壞輕鐵站有關。警方透露，在搜屋期間警員搜出 31 個玻璃樽，以及89張現金券等。<br />\n<br />\n有關案件涉及六人，早前一對姓梁 21 歲成年孖生兄弟被指涉案，案件押至1月30日再訊，以索取法律文件及意見。控罪指該對孖生兄弟在 9 月 7 日在天水圍輕鐵濕地公園站，串謀另外4人非法損壞屬於港鐵公司的財產，即一部八達通機、兩部售票機，及兩部輕鐵資料顯示屏，令玻璃螢幕碎裂，以及在兩個閉路電視噴上紅色噴漆，以上這些設施的維修費超過27萬元。<br />\n<br />\n二人原被控損壞財產罪，後被改控刑事毀壞，現時獲准繼續保釋。而警方短片所指被拘捕的男子，相信是孖生兄弟串謀的另外 4 人中的其中人。不過該案並不涉及氣油彈攻擊，未知警方披露涉案人士家中搜出玻璃樽和現金券，和案情的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%BF%95%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6-%E5%86%8D%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA-%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA-31-%E5%80%8B%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%A8%BD-89-%E5%BC%B5%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25BF%2595%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA-31-%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%258E%25BB%25E7%2592%2583%25E6%25A8%25BD-89-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2588%25B8%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=ee598699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25BF%2595%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA-31-%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%258E%25BB%25E7%2592%2583%25E6%25A8%25BD-89-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2588%25B8%2F&h=355d6b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%BF%95%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E6%A1%88-%E8%AD%A6-%E5%86%8D%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA-%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA-31-%E5%80%8B%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%A8%BD-89-%E5%BC%B5%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"fe322ee46ebf88b71cfd6869fb42d658aaf40028","tid":1816542,"uid":8423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"孖生！？<br />\n咁你點證明邊個打邊個？"},{"pid":"2b36afef1fdc215a2bacf78793274de4cf48c67a","tid":1816542,"uid":214635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"大撚把人飲酒飲牛奶都留中把樽啦on9，現金券我老母銀包都十幾張以上，好心你話下次搜到火箭炮好過"},{"pid":"c12cee9de909a304cce0aa75cc6215d33ab3dd8c","tid":1816542,"uid":175731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"玻璃樽？屋企有刀有火機有酒點算"},{"pid":"e092b030a70707788e5b47c929c572f291a448c7","tid":1816542,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60d52bd27e800c97998a578e17a7621f67b706e5","tid":1816542,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"現金券關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9926715749ee88de411ca31f8f4ac9dcd3d6afe4","tid":1816542,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"呢排無咩行動，唔好收埋咁多野係屋企，唔好比班狗有藉口告到"},{"pid":"e7165d187346675644a5e86172f8dfcb740138c8","tid":1816542,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60d52bd27e800c97998a578e17a7621f67b706e5","tid":1816542,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited